
Anaconda:
conda config --set auto_activate_base false
source deactivate / conda deactivate - move from anaconda environment
deactivate - move from a virtual environment

virtualenv - python2
pip install virtualenv
python -m virtualenv ~/.virtualenvs/soap # in case python 2 is the default python version in your system
(specifies that we're creating a virtual environment - soap - in .virtualenvs folder which is in the home directory)  
or
python2 -m virtualenv ~/.virtualenvs/soap

venv - python3
python -m venv ~/.virtualenvs/soap  # in case python 3 is the default python version in your system
or
python3 -m venv ~/.virtualenvs/soap



